channel.title: Stairways is out!
channel.description:
My largely anticipated second album “Stairways” has finally been released! It’s on SoundCloud, and it will be up on all platforms soon. https://soundcloud.com/vokonmusic/sets/stairways
Tracklist:
Cutoff (w/ mr serpent) Ratios Ragnarok Broken Traces (w/ azure onyxscore) Insomnia Bromine Chambers Stairways (w/ hern) Kill the President Implode (w/ Arimyth) Summer Serpentine
Thanks to everyone who helped along the way of this record! Just a few people who helped a ton are Peregrihn, Mr. Serpent, Pristinity, Electrify, Davidnaha, isg (of GLACIERS), azure, hern, arimyth, and hurlybird
